{"tid":2284624,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2020DSE作文題目-送禮之我見求意見","createTime":"2020-11-13T12:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T03:54:12.000Z","uid":326076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87f58687fa3f7859c4bf36f03a77aa5d2b6b40fc","tid":2284624,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"小弟作文成日都得5嘅水平 上唔到*<br />\n之前試過試作送禮之我見<br />\n我間學校個老師就同我講我作嘅<br />\n立論-&gt;論點-&gt;歸納太過平鋪直敍+論點角度太單一<br />\n所以想重新作一次試下<br />\n今次我想用以下結構去作:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立論:<br />\n背景 定義<br />\n送禮是人與人之間藉以表達心意維繫關係的重要手段，當今社會的人大多不得要領。<br />\n<br />\n分論點1<br />\n1.1籍送禮與親近的人關係更進一步<br />\n1.2藉送禮與不和的人冰釋前嫌<br />\n1.3藉送禮與萍水相逢的人結下善緣<br />\n<br />\n轉折<br />\n<br />\n分論點2<br />\n送禮的本質-&gt;今人大多為鸚鵡學舌-&gt;未能真正瞭解背後意義並且知行合一 -&gt;寄語讀者<br />\n<br />\n如果咁先立後破得唔得?<br />\n定其實依然有單一+線性呢個問題?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求各位指教 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ad0c50584f1fda18857f7e7e90d1a912dbc47c","tid":2284624,"uid":326076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:19:14.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"83420bd7be0978267c8f56f4922c4c5683141a16","tid":2284624,"uid":317874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b16114f7a5bcff06b11493f03273a34c682462a","tid":2284624,"uid":317874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4755d908efccbb4667d79d6e9ee8464c9caa144","tid":2284624,"uid":166947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83420bd7be0978267c8f56f4922c4c5683141a16","tid":2284624,"uid":317874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"648931a28a38711119ee99b4e508e6118722b08a","tid":2284624,"uid":166947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"睇你大綱係ok嘅，至於會唔會太單調/平舖直敘，就睇你嘅文筆同你引嘅例子啦<br />\n<br />\n我個人覺得如果文章可以緊貼時事，會更加有吸引力，好過響個架空時間咁天馬行空式作幻想例子"},{"pid":"a16b9377a99627c28bf83b2c259bc0d860de2d5d","tid":2284624,"uid":366192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"補欣屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34917a01ce18be881611aaa2b289859968731d1b","tid":2284624,"uid":208552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"分論點2有少少似總結，同埋知行合一唔太適合呢篇文"},{"pid":"285fb14caa8bd8216ecaf512cab81cbb0010994e","tid":2284624,"uid":305518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T02:54:44.000Z","msg":"有冇用李克勤做例子先"},{"pid":"72797f10e34a9f4dccb1625a9b4754fc0f938e28","tid":2284624,"uid":367849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T03:54:12.000Z","msg":"睇標題以為係玩嘢，原來係認真問"}]}